Titolo: Atelier Marie: The Alchemist of Salburg

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Atelier Marie: The Alchemist of Salburg is a role-playing video game developed by Gust Co. Ltd., and the first title within the Atelier game series. It was first released on the PlayStation and, soon after, ported to the Sega Saturn and Microsoft Windows, eventually being bundled alongside Atelier Elie for the Sega Dreamcast and later PlayStation 2. It has not been released outside Japan. However, a fan translation of the PlayStation 2 bundle was completed in 2018.